<% content_for :title do %>About | <%= installation_brand_name %><% end %>
<% content_for :meta_description do %>
  <%= installation_brand_name %> is a customer support platform by SamaBrains Solutions. Connect Gmail, social messaging,
  and website chat so your team can manage customer conversations in one workspace.
<% end %>

<h1>About <%= installation_brand_name %></h1>
<p class="updated">Customer support platform by <strong>SamaBrains Solutions</strong></p>

<p>
  <strong><%= installation_brand_name %></strong> is a cloud-based customer support and shared inbox platform.
  Businesses use it to read and reply to customer messages from connected channels in a single workspace,
  assign conversations to agents, and deliver faster, more organized support.
</p>

<h2>Who it is for</h2>
<p>
  <%= installation_brand_name %> is built for <strong>businesses and their support teams</strong>—not for individual
  consumers signing up for personal use. Workspace owners connect their communication channels; agents and
  administrators collaborate inside the product to respond to customers.
</p>

<h2>What you can do</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Manage customer conversations from one dashboard</li>
  <li>Connect <strong>Gmail</strong> inboxes to receive and send support email</li>
  <li>Connect <strong>Facebook Messenger</strong> and <strong>Instagram</strong> direct messages</li>
  <li>Embed <strong>live chat</strong> on your website</li>
  <li>Assign conversations to team members and track response activity</li>
  <li>Use help center and automation features where enabled on your plan</li>
</ul>

<h2>How Gmail and Google sign-in work</h2>
<p>
  When you choose to connect a <strong>Gmail inbox</strong>, <%= installation_brand_name %> requests access through
  Google OAuth so agents can read incoming support mail and send replies on your behalf. We use Gmail access only
  for the inbox you connect—not for advertising or unrelated purposes. You can revoke access at any time in your
  <a href="https://myaccount.google.com/permissions" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Account permissions</a>.
</p>
<p>
  Optional <strong>Sign in with Google</strong> lets workspace users authenticate with their Google account instead
  of a password, using standard email and profile scopes only.
</p>

<h2>Data and privacy</h2>
<p>
  Conversation data stays within your workspace. We process information as described in our
  <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>. Third-party channels (Google, Meta, and others) process data under their
  own policies when you enable those integrations.
</p>

<h2>Get started</h2>
<p>
  Existing users can <a href="/app/login">sign in</a>. New organizations can
  <a href="/app/auth/signup">create a workspace</a> if signup is enabled on this installation.
</p>

